Subject: files still not uploading on website after whitelisting that website
Description:
Files still not uploading on website after whitelisting that website, checked and found that it is showing blocked with the error:  "Web Upload*[JS_ENABLED_FLAG]"
Although we were able to upload the files on this website before upgrading it from 5.9.3.0 to 5.9.4.0
Solution_Comment__c: Deselected the Unidentified File type from the policy and it worked ok after that
